{"word":"H1144 - בִּנְיָמִין - Binyâmîyn - bin-yaw-mene' - Benjamin","slug":"H1144","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">בִּנְיָמִין</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>Binyâmîyn"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>bin-yaw-mene'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Benjamin"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"Original: <b><he>בּנימין</he></b> <p />Transliteration: <b>binyâmı̂yn</b> <p />Phonetic: <b>bin-yaw-mene'</b> <p class=\"bdb_def\"><b>BDB Definition</b>:</p> Benjamin = \"son of the right hand\" <ol><li>Jacob's and Rachel's youngest son, Joseph's full brother</li><li>son of Bilhan, great-grandson of Benjamin</li><li>a Benjamite, one of the sons of Harim, in the time of Ezra who had taken a strange wife</li><li>the tribe descended from Benjamin, the son of Jacob</li></ol> <p />Origin: from <a href=\"#/H1121\">H1121</a> and <a href=\"#/H3225\">H3225</a> <p />TWOT entry: <a class=\"T\" href=\"S:0254 - ben\">254a</a> <p />Part(s) of speech: Proper Name Masculine "},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H1121\">H1121</a>, <a href=\"#/H1122\">H1122</a>, <a href=\"#/H1125\">H1125</a>, <a href=\"#/H1126\">H1126</a>, <a href=\"#/H1127\">H1127</a>, <a href=\"#/H1128\">H1128</a>, <a href=\"#/H1130\">H1130</a>, <a href=\"#/H1132\">H1132</a>, <a href=\"#/H1133\">H1133</a>, <a href=\"#/H1134\">H1134</a>, <a href=\"#/H1135\">H1135</a>, <a href=\"#/H1136\">H1136</a>, <a href=\"#/H1139\">H1139</a>, <a href=\"#/H1142\">H1142</a>, <a href=\"#/H1145\">H1145</a>, <a href=\"#/H1148\">H1148</a>, <a href=\"#/H1151\">H1151</a>, <a href=\"#/H1323\">H1323</a>, <a href=\"#/H1332\">H1332</a>, <a href=\"#/H1337\">H1337</a>, <a href=\"#/H1339\">H1339</a>, <a href=\"#/H1340\">H1340</a>, <a href=\"#/H2618\">H2618</a>"}]}